phdl.parser
Class PhdlWalker

java.lang.Object
  org.antlr.runtime.BaseRecognizer
      org.antlr.runtime.tree.TreeParser
          phdl.parser.PhdlWalker

public class PhdlWalker
extends org.antlr.runtime.tree.TreeParser

A tree grammar that walks a the output of the PHDL parser. It operates on a stream of tree nodes of the form (parent child1 child2 ... childN) where each node may be the root of another subtree.

Version:
0.1
Author:
Richard Black and Brad Riching
